@0    = ~Bring me Alassa, the thief.~
@1    = ~I can't change your mind, <CHARNAME>, but do not forget that what you do may affect others as well.~
@2    = ~By no means would I find it an easy choice myself. The power of a god isn't something to be turned down lightly...and yet I would miss the pleasures of the flesh.~
@3    = ~Tell me about Alassa.~
@4    = ~Seductive temptress, the name of beautiful Alassa is whispered and feared across the Realms. Many a man would dream of her company, and yet few would dare chance it.~
@5    = ~Few would dare chance it? I don't know what you've heard about me, but it's not like I'm a man-eater!~
